    <h2>Article 1 (Purpose)</h2>
    <p>These terms set out the conditions and procedures for using all services provided by Rabbit Logs (the "Blog"), as well as the rights, obligations, and responsibilities of the Blog and its users, and other necessary matters.</p>

    <h2>Article 2 (Definitions)</h2>
