      <li>Content: all posts, images, code, video, and other material published on the Blog.</li>
      <li>Operator: the party that creates, manages, and writes the Blog.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Article 3 (Effect and Amendment of Terms)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>These terms apply to all users who access the Blog and take effect upon being posted.</li>
      <li>If a user continues to use the service, they are deemed to have agreed to these terms.</li>
      <li>The Operator may amend these terms within the limits of applicable law.</li>
      <li>When amending, the Operator will announce the effective date and reason, along with the current terms, on the Blog from seven days before the effective date.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Article 4 (Copyright and Use of Content)</h2>
