      <li>Intentionally disrupting the operation of the Blog (e.g., distributing malware, hacking).</li>
      <li>Distributing information, text, or images that violate public order or good morals.</li>
      <li>Any other unlawful or improper conduct.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Article 8 (Governing Law and Jurisdiction)</h2>
